Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:05.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:13.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:36.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:40.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:42.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:52.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:01:01.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:05.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:09.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:11.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:18.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:28.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:33.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:37.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,morning, Ichigo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to attack your own son\Nin his sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:53.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about Karin and\NYuzu's injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Injuries? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:01.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A truck crashes into our house,\Nand no one's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's more miraculous is\Nthat no one woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What's going on? Their wounds...\N– And the culprit gone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– They're all gone.\N– Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– He'll probably come to apologize later.\N– Everyone thinks it was some truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:21.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:25.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the work of\Na Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:29.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, hurry and eat breakfast\Nor you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she went back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to that place she called\Nthe Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime, did you bring lunch today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:56.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have taiyaki-style ramen\N with wasabi and honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some, Tatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:02.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err...no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:08.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:12.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you bumped into her and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that's all you can say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:18.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:29.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have voby...bolley...volley...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a mean look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:39.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why're you so late?\NIt's already lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:50.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, I heard a truck crashed\Ninto your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:53.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Finished cleaning up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err...no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad, you'll end up destroying\Nthe place even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Modern literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:20.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sitting next to you from today.\NMy name's Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, this is our first meeting.\NRight, Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a transfer student, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:35.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:44.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! Just what the hell\Nare you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, how scary! What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to do\Nsomething to me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, quit talking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:57.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think this is pretty good\Nconsidering I learned it overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:00.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! So why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:04.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going back to\Nthat Soul Society or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only Soul Reapers can\Ngo back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:11.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I don't have that ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:18.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, most of my powers\Nas a Soul Reaper were taken by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:19.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything\Nabout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:25.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,\NI'm stuck in this gigai form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's a "gigai"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:31.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a temporary body provided\Nfor use in emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers who are drastically\Nweakened inhabit a gigai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,until their powers return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:41.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my classmates\Ncould see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:44.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,until my powers return,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:50.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you will have to do\Nthe work of a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have the powers\Nof a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– to refuse.\N– I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to fight\Nsuch monsters again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:06.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! You did fine yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's because my family was\Nbeing attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not about to fight\Nfor complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:21.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:22.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aghh! My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:47.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An order...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:56.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Whole spirit who lives\Nin this park will probably be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:07.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going to help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:14.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he a complete stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stand here when\Nhe's being attacked before my very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:23.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper must treat\Nall spirits equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just because they're close by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:33.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,just because it's convenient...\Nit doesn't work like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you intend to help that boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:40.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,make up your mind\Nto save all spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must make the commitment\Nto go anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and even be willing to\Nsacrifice your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you committed to this, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about commitment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:30.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I saved this boy because I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:33.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You risked your life to\Nsave me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think about your duty\Nas a Soul Reaper when you acted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you put yourself at risk,\Nit doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will be different!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want another\Nscary experience like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hurry up and pass over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was a fine Konso.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:31.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you intend\Nto do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wandering spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:10.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Devour it...that man's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:18.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me God... Why was I born?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:10.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please summon me back\Nto your side! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am studying\Ncontemporary language!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't sound contemporary\Nat all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, how long are you\Ngonna keep following me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until you agree to do\Nthe Soul Reaper's job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:33.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:36.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did that car just hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:45.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe? And you're okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was just a little bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:53.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine? And where's the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:53.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It drove away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:06.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:07.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! She's in our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's Inoue! Orihime Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:16.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hello, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been out shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes! Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:29.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My leeks, butter, bananas,\Nand bean jam...they're fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is she gonna make with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that bruise on your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I just get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe when the car hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That looks bad, it must hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A little. But I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...\NWhat's the matter, Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You look so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:01.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to walk you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:14.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes! She'd better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean, Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:33.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you good friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. I've never even\Nspoken to her much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's close to one of my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who lives in\Nthe neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:43.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:51.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago...\Nher brother died at our hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was her only family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die! Please don't\Nleave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:14.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that\Nshe was the girl who was crying that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just found out recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How was your spirit energy\Nat that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Not as strong as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:26.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's only recently that I've been able\Nto see ghosts and talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:40.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Tatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom asked me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's stewed beef with potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:02.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Home-made stewed beef\Nand potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You eat such weird stuff\Nwhen you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen my pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, at least knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:32.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you've gotten so mean now\Nthat you're in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know where\Nyour pajamas are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. My dress is also missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you have to ask\Nme about everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An order?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:56.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:03.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing there?!\NAnd those pajamas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Save it for later. We have an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:08.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!\NIt's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't just swing\Nthe sword around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! As long as I kill it, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:00.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not deep enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:01.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It got away. We're going after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:37.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was Inoue's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking a Hollow from behind\Nand splitting its head in one blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the essence of\Nexterminating a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:30.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is to minimize your own injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:39.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and also so that you never\Nsee the identity of the Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:42.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean\N"identity of the Hollow"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:51.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All Hollows were once\Nthe souls of ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:52.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You never told me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that just some monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Some monster we needed to kill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, now he is just a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And he must be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But... he was once human...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Grudges, regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:20.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Souls who still harbor such feelings\Nare hard to perform Konso on,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:21.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and linger on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:25.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then they either become\NHollows themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or are devoured by other Hollows,\Nand become new Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:42.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But they were just\Nwalking together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why that Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize he was\Nsuch a fast worker...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even walk you home\Neven though you were hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:55.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, he offered to\Nwalk me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aghh! Watch out! I'm going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Champ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you imagining?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the right! Yes, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! It's a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:04.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:08.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:14.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:19.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:23.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:28.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:40.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:43.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am the charismatic seer\Nof the new century!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:46.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The messenger from\Nthe Netherworld, Don Kanonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:50.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I journey everywhere\Nin search of bad spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:53.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your cue yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:54.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of time, again!